5. How to compress multiple files?
We can use the following command-
Syntax: tar -czvf <filename.tar.gz> <file1.txt> <file2.txt> <file3.txt>
ex: In the below example, we use the command “tar -czvf namelstupdated.tar.gz file1.txt file2.txt” to compress multiple files
 


